<tr><td><strong>Ease of Use</strong></td><td>⭐⭐⭐ Steep learning curve</td><td>⭐⭐⭐⭐ Cleaner, more intuitive</td><td>⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ Most beginner-friendly</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>Pricing (Pro)</strong></td><td>$129.95/mo</td><td>$129/mo (Lite plan)</td><td>$99/mo (Standard plan)</td></tr>
